title: Chedd's Gourmet Grilled Cheese Closing
text:
Chedd's Gourmet Grilled Cheese Closing October 15, 2015, 9:50 AM by Angela Kennecke SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
Phillips Avenue is losing a restaurant. Chedd's Gourmet Grilled Cheese is closing its doors after more than five years in business. Calls to the restaurant went unanswered, but on its Facebook page, Chedd's says it will remain open through the end of November. 
Chedd's restaurants in Denver, Colorado, and Austin, Texas, also closed a few years ago.
